&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Test session details:&lt;br/&gt;
clients: &lt;a href=&quot;https://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-master/4336&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-master/4336&lt;/a&gt; - 4.18.0-348.7.1.el8_5.x86_64&lt;br/&gt;
servers: &lt;a href=&quot;https://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-b2_14/2&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-b2_14/2&lt;/a&gt; - 4.18.0-240.1.1.el8_lustre.x86_64&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;it looks like this first started failing in interop testing in 2022-08-09&lt;/p&gt;







